original_title: AAA Buzz Communication Tour 2011 Deluxe Edition
overview: AAA BUZZ COMMUNICATION TOUR 2011 DELUXE EDITION is the sixteenth concert DVD and nineteenth overall video released by AAA. This DVD contains the footage of a concert held at SAITAMA SUPER ARENA on June 26th 2011. First press editions comes with two postcards. The DVD charted for 10 weeks and peaked #2 on Oricon Music DVD Charts.
title: AAA Buzz Communication Tour 2011 Deluxe Edition
